\N<Rozaro>What's wrong, Riia? Why are you here... It's unusual. Are
you alright?
\N<Riia>...

\N<Rozaro>...You must have a lot on your mind. But don't let it show
on your face. You'll be at a loss if you go around showing
hostility to everyone indiscriminately.

to think I've given you plenty of guidance. Are you saying
even that relationship has been destroyed?
\N<Riia>...Somehow... I just can't sleep...

me.

\N<Rozaro>I see... You witnessed that battle, huh? And your childhood
friend was defeated right before your eyes. That must have
been very hard for you.

\N<Riia>...Mom said it's going to be okay, but... what happens to
the person who lost...?

\N<Rozaro>Indeed, as your mother says, they probably won't take their
lives. But, it's as if their dignity as a person has been
taken away. Especially the women are likely to receive such
treatment.
\N<Riia>Such... treatment?
